The following modifications were made:
  - Added `leafnode` module to async-nats crate implementing a NATS
    leaf node gateway server (TCP accept loop, server-side protocol
    handling, subscription routing with wildcard matching, and upstream
    hub connection support).
  - Added `Serialize` derive to `ServerInfo` struct.
  - Added `Deserialize` derive to `ConnectInfo` struct.
